## 🔥 High Priority - Should Use Now

### 1. **Suggestion Component** ✨
**Status**: ✅ Already installed, not used yet

**What it does**: Displays clickable suggestion pills that users can tap to quickly send common prompts.

**Why you need it**:
- Improve UX for new users who don't know what to ask
- Reduce typing friction
- Guide users to discover agent capabilities
- Perfect for empty state in new chats

**Implementation Example**:
```tsx
// In ChatMessagesPanel.tsx (empty state section)
import { Suggestions, Suggestion } from "@/components/ai-elements/suggestion";

const mediaSuggestions = [
  "Create a sunset beach image",
  "Generate a product demo video",
  "Remove background from my logo",
  "Upscale this image to 4K",
];

// In empty state:
{showEmptyState && (
  <div className="flex-center flex-col gap-4">
    <h2>No conversations yet</h2>
    <Suggestions>
      {mediaSuggestions.map((suggestion) => (
        <Suggestion
          key={suggestion}
          suggestion={suggestion}
          onClick={(text) => sendMessage({ role: "user", parts: [{ type: "text", text }] })}
        />
      ))}
    </Suggestions>
  </div>
)}
```

**Files to modify**:
- `src/components/product/editor/agent/ChatMessagesPanel.tsx`

**Benefits**:
- ✅ Zero-friction onboarding
- ✅ Discoverability of features
- ✅ Reduced empty state friction

